end of creamy chocolate and luscious caramel, reminiscent of the beloved Cobbers.</p>\n    \n    <h3>International Delights</h3>\n    <p>Introduce some global flair with <a href=\"https://sweetsworld.com.au/candy/american-candy/american-chocolate/lolliland-choco-rocks/\">Lolliland Choco Rocks</a>, perfect for adding a crunchy, chocolatey surprise to your candy selection.</p>\n\n    \n    <aside class=\"seo-product-gallery\" style=\"margin: 36px 0; padding: 18px; background: #f8fbfd; border: 1px solid #e5eef5; border-radius: 20px;\">\n        <p style=\"margin: 0 0 10px; font-size: 0.72rem; letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase; font-weight: 700; color: #7aa9c2;\">You may also want to buy</p>\n        <ul style=\"display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(180px, 1fr)); gap: 14px; list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0;\">\n            <li class=\"seo-product-card\" style=\"background: #fff; border: 1px solid #e7edf3; border-radius: 16px; padding: 14px; box-shadow: 0 1px 2px rgba(31, 52, 73, 0.04);\"><a href=\"https://sweetsworld.com.au/candy/american-candy/american-chocolate/lolliland-choco-rocks/\" style=\"text-decoration: none; color: inherit; display: block;\"><img src=\"https://sweetsworld.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/Lolliland-Chocolate-Rocks-1kg.jpg\" alt=\"Lolliland Choco Rocks 1kg\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"width: 100%; max-width: 180px; aspect-ratio: 1 / 1; object-fit: contain; display: block; margin: 0 auto 12px;\" /><span style=\"display: block; font-size: 0.98rem; line-height: 1.4; margin: 0; color: #3b4b5c;\">Lolliland Choco Rocks 1kg</span><span style=\"display: block; margin-top: 8px; font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.95rem; color: #6bb6d9;\">$29.99</span></a></li>\n            <li class=\"seo-product-card\" style=\"background: #fff; border: 1px solid #e7edf3; border-radius: 16px; padding: 14px; box-shadow: 0 1px 2px rgba(31, 52, 73, 0.04);\"><a href=\"https://sweetsworld.com.au/chocolate/australian-chocolate/milk-choc